{"tid":704945,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 剛過60大壽　貨Van司機深水埗落貨　遭水車從後撞斃","createTime":"2018-06-16T17:15:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T05:03:41.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"04aa64c16544dd09549b6ee4e0e0ce4afeb36763","tid":704945,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T17:15:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1551033/org/a3417faa0763fa74f24101a47e517055.jpg/swMB8M0xcCwL9ujF2xJewNKy6ouAh1Tv8ZNcCPGTXAg?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1551033%2Forg%2Fa3417faa0763fa74f24101a47e517055.jpg%2FswMB8M0xcCwL9ujF2xJewNKy6ouAh1Tv8ZNcCPGTXAg%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=fd249715&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今(16日)晚上8時許，深水埗北河街及醫局街交界，一輛客貨車停泊上址，<span style=\"color: red;\">司機下車後疑打開車底門落貨</span>，其間一輛水車從後開車，疑未有察覺客貨車司機，將他撞倒。客貨車被撞至衝前數米，另一名站在前方的非華裔男子疑閃避不及，被客貨車撞倒。客貨車車尾門被撞至扭曲，橫亙路中。而水車的擋風玻璃破裂。<br />\n<br />\n客貨車司機左邊下半身被輾過，傷勢嚴重，由救護車送往瑪嘉烈醫院搶救，惟返魂乏術，證實不治。而非華裔男子則受傷，清醒送往明愛醫院。警方正調查意外原因。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指，死者上月剛過六十大壽，詎料遇上車禍喪命。司機家屬得悉意外後，趕至現場了解。一名年輕男子情緒激動，到場後大叫﹕「邊個撞佢!」更一度衝向水車司機，被交通警員制止。事後家屬相擁痛哭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/200208/%E5%A5%AA%E5%91%BD%E8%BB%8A%E7%A6%8D-%E5%89%9B%E9%81%8E60%E5%A4%A7%E5%A3%BD-%E8%B2%A8van%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97%E8%90%BD%E8%B2%A8-%E9%81%AD%E6%B0%B4%E8%BB%8A%E5%BE%9E%E5%BE%8C%E6%92%9E%E6%96%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F200208%2F%25E5%25A5%25AA%25E5%2591%25BD%25E8%25BB%258A%25E7%25A6%258D-%25E5%2589%259B%25E9%2581%258E60%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25A3%25BD-%25E8%25B2%25A8van%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%259F%2597%25E8%2590%25BD%25E8%25B2%25A8-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%25BE%259E%25E5%25BE%258C%25E6%2592%259E%25E6%2596%2583&d=SN79dnOdyUqSvXT8OLBezePnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=5b260139\" data-auto-